How to Excel Automation using Power Automation Desktop-
 Some of the Action we learn ,those are using excel automation.

Use Case 1. We have data in excel file about employe information, now that excel file convert to .txt file.
            now discuss one by one step how can we do.
             For Coverting simple step here- 
               a. Lunch the excel
               b. Read from Excel work sheet
               c.if excel file read after that write the data in txt file (Write text to a file)
               d. after that close excel.
Use case 2. How to write data in excel 
        step- a. Lunch the excel
              b. Write to excel worksheet
              c. close Excel
